<article id="cas">
  <title>GT &shortversion;: Community Authorization Service (CAS)</title>
  <titleabbrev>Community Authorization Service (CAS)</titleabbrev>
  <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="WS_AA_CAS_Overview_Brief_Frag.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(/section/*)"/>
  <informaltable frame="none">
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <colspec colname="c1"/>
      <colspec colname="c2"/>
      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry namest="c1" nameend="c2">The following guides are available for this
            component:</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>
            <ulink url="http://gdp.globus.org/gt4-tutorial/">The Globus Toolkit 4 Programmer's
              Tutorial</ulink>
          </entry>
          <entry> Useful tutorial about programming with Web Services in GT4. </entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>
            
              <emphasis role="strong">
                <olink targetdoc="securityKey">Security Key Concepts</olink>
              </emphasis>
            
          </entry>
          <entry>For important general concepts.</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>
            <emphasis role="strong">
              <olink targetdoc="casAdmin">Admin Guide</olink>
            </emphasis>
          </entry>
          <entry>For system administrators and those installing, building and deploying GT, contains
            information specific to CAS system administrators. You should already have read Installing the
            [Globus Toolkit] and [Quickstart].</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>
            <emphasis role="strong">
              <olink targetdoc="casUser">User's Guide</olink>
            </emphasis>
          </entry>
          <entry>For end-users (such as scientists). Be sure to also
            read the [GT User Guide] for important general info.</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>
            <emphasis role="strong">
              <olink targetdoc="casDeveloper">Developer's Guide</olink>
            </emphasis>
          </entry>
          <entry>For developers (or advanced end-users) who want to [fixme].</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry namest="c1" nameend="c2">Other information available for this component
            are:</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>
            <emphasis role="strong">
              <olink targetdoc="casRN">Release Notes</olink>
            </emphasis>
          </entry>
          <entry>What's new with the &version; release for this component.</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>
            <emphasis role="strong">
              <olink targetdoc="casPI">Public Interface Guide</olink>
            </emphasis>
          </entry>
          <entry>Information for all public interfaces (including APIs, commands, WSDL, etc). Please
            note this is a subset of information in the <olink targetdoc="casDeveloper"
              >Developer's Guide</olink>.</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>
            <emphasis role="strong">
              <olink targetdoc="casQP">Quality Profile</olink>
            </emphasis>
          </entry>
          <entry>Information about test coverage reports, etc.</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>
            <emphasis role="strong">
              <olink targetdoc="casMig">Migrating Guide</olink>
            </emphasis>
          </entry>
          <entry>Information for migrating to this version if you were using a previous version of
            GT.</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>
